{"tid":1979953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣一票站容納1200人投票 香港一張檯就要容納1500人投票","createTime":"2020-04-19T19:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T01:43:20.000Z","uid":210495,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"793e1c72389e101268154250efcdf2953170da84","tid":1979953,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T19:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200109/s00004/30462ba8e199c9ef3d16d8821c3391bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200109%2Fs00004%2F30462ba8e199c9ef3d16d8821c3391bb.jpg&h=d6d0d83b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote>全台票站總數達17,232個；又擴大選民分流，每個票站的投票人數規模由1500人減到1200人；投票間也由九合一選舉時的公投兩個、選舉兩個，增至4至6個，且票站愈大投票間愈多；動員逾22萬名選務人員，以確保投票順利舉行。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5GDROh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5GDROh.png&h=69bef875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地成間學校做一個票點都係畀1200人投票 又唔洗排咁耐<br />\n仲動員22萬公務員去幫手 <br />\n<br />\n香港人投票都賤過地底泥<br />\n一張投票檯 (即係對身分證果d檯) 都已經要serve 1500人<br />\n唔怪得知區選果陣排曬長龍<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">根本一個票站就唔應該serve咁多人</span></span></strong><br />\n用台灣票站數目做比對<br />\n香港應該要用4500個票站<br />\n但係區選果陣先得610個一般投票站及23個專用投票站 (狗屋 &amp; 懲教院所)<br />\n<br />\n如果用台灣個比例香港應該要動員5萬幾個公務員係投票日去幫手<br />\n但係宜家先得3萬 (黑警唔計)"},{"pid":"7a8e95fbab5a1c51c6464a72f61ee02a0a0c6e0b","tid":1979953,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T19:26:36.000Z","msg":"極權政府會認真對待投票咩?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港獨立 唯一出路</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a4ab64962389327e2cda04d01f22afbdd0b766e2","tid":1979953,"uid":4156,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T19:28:08.000Z","msg":"on9仔 香港幾大台灣幾大呀"},{"pid":"df4c807432b6a3f6d833bd54796915c8fa33b374","tid":1979953,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4ab